{"tid":2181139,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：任何人都會犯錯，法官也不例外","createTime":"2020-08-30T11:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T12:17:47.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"02c856b59fc1282ba9f0e4c8de0d6369453f4f2d","tid":2181139,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546821-20200830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546821-20200830.htm&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoNTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=0e1333a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546821-20200830.htm&h=2b9efeab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546821-20200830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊表示，法官的職責是按法律和證據審理案件，但任何人都會犯錯，法官也不例外，在某些情況下控辯雙方需要考慮就裁決提出上訴，當法官在法律觀點上犯錯、錯誤運用酌情權，或者由於嚴重的程序或其他失當而導致裁決不公，律政司就要決定是否對案件提出上訴，或者申請覆核刑期等，而律政司的所有決定都是根據法律原則和法庭程序，以及經過仔細研究整體案情後才作出。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊在網誌又說，理性和建設性討論法庭裁決有助提升社會對法治概念的意識，但有時市民太著重案件的結果，而忽略了闡述判決的法律和證據基礎，認為市民應該避免以偏概全，不應只根據片面之詞便妄下定論。"},{"pid":"624fb6df0b8da1f9c78cc5dd950916d965e30360","tid":2181139,"uid":212884,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"014ed641adef341a5aa7ea775260a3b39fb24f7b","tid":2181139,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"624fb6df0b8da1f9c78cc5dd950916d965e30360","tid":2181139,"uid":212884,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港共法治"},{"pid":"a28e9fd6f9bcdff209b6b20f2db4e12d92c02ad8","tid":2181139,"uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"咁鄭若驊犯錯點搞？"},{"pid":"aed01518fd471657f262ba5c901b02981fc77a29","tid":21811